        "Description": "Start as Ninja. Bring coins and keycard hackers/scramblers. You can do the ninja assassination with shuriken challenge. Alternatively, you can do the Cottonmouth challenge as the Motoryclist for both assassinations instead. Destroy the camera on the corner where the two guards sit and leave from by the rockway down to the hospital. Go the direction the guards went and go instead the first door to the right. Go downstairs to the morgue. Lure one guard at a time into the hallway behind. Kill them.",
